quran[59]{c,v,t}:
  44,1,Ha Mim
  44,2,Nditsuba khushitabu shinoosinjia
  44,3,"Toto\tefwe\tkhwashishia\tmushilo shietsikhabi, toto efwe khuli abekanyilisi"
  44,4,Toto ishilo esho buli likhuwa eliamachesi linoosibungwa
  44,5,Likhuwa lirula khwifwe toto efwe nefwe Abaruma
  44,6,"Tsimbabaasi okhurula khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, toto ye ni Omuwulili Omumanyi muno"
  44,7,"Nyasaye Omulesi welikulu nende eshialo nende biosi bili hakari wabio, toto nimuli mbu enywe muli nende obwatieli"
  44,8,"Abulaho Nyasaye wundi tawe halali Ye, alamusinjia ne afwisinjia Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi nende Owabasenywe beyimbeli"
  44,9,Halali bo bali mutsinganakani babayanga
  44,10,Kho linda inyanga yelikulu liakharusie omwosi kulolekha
  44,11,"Kulifunikha Abandu, shino ni eshinyasio eshilulu"
  44,12,"Nyasaye Omulesi wefu, khuyiniliekhwo eshinyasio toto efwe nibasuubila"
  44,13,"Okhwitsulila khwabu khubakhoonya shina bulano, ne toto Omurumwa Omwinoosia yamala okhubeetsela"
  44,14,"Mana nibamukalukhanilia obweni, nibaboola mbu: “ uno yechesibwa, naye ni Omulalu.”"
  44,15,"Toto efwe khwitsa okhuyiniaho eshinyasio hatiti, netoto enywe mulakalukha shinga mwali"
  44,16,Inyanga yakhulikhupa eshikhupo eshikhongo toto efwe khulibarunga
  44,17,"Netoto efwe khwakholela Abandu ba Firaun amatemo imbeli wabu, neyaboolela Omurumwa Woluyali"
  44,18,"Naboola mbu: “Mumbe Abasumba ba Nyasaye, toto esie endi Omurumwa Omwisikwa khwinywe”"
  44,19,"Ne mulakholela Nyasaye obufuru tawe, toto esie ndalabarerera ebifune biyela"
  44,20,Ne esie ndiliinda khu Nyasaye wanje Omulesi ninanyu mulandasa amachina tawe
  44,21,"Ne nimulasuubila tawe , mube ehale ninasi"
  44,22,"Nasaba Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi mbu: “toto bano ni Abandu abamabii.”"
  44,23,"Mana Nyasaye naboola mbu: “orule nende Abasumba banje eshilo, toto enywe mulalondwakhwo.”"
  44,24,"Ne oleshe inyanza endio ngayilekhaane, Toto abo ni omukanda kweliyie kwitsa okhusishibwa"
  44,25,Ne balekha emikunda chinga nende tsisebele
  44,26,Nende emimela nende obwami bwoluyali
  44,27,Nende obwokholo bwabasangalilanga
  44,28,"Endio nilwakali, mana nikhuhelesia ako Abandu bandi"
  44,29,"Ne likulu nohomba eshialo sishiabalilila tawe, ne shibahebwa ebise tawe"
  44,30,Ne toto khwahabina Abana ba Israeil khushinyasio shiokhubatutuyia
  44,31,"Okhurula khu Firauni, toto ye yali Omufuru mubalia babura eshichelo"
  44,32,"Ne toto khwabalobola khumachesi kefu, okhushila ebilonje bindi khushialo"
  44,33,Ne nikhubahelesia ebimanyisio biefu amatemo kalolekha
  44,34,Toto bano baboolanga mbu
  44,35,"Khubulaho okhufwa khundi tawe halali okhufwa khweimbeli, ne efwe shikhulilamusibwa tawe"
  44,36,Mana lamusiekhwo Basefwe nikali mbu muboolanga habwene
  44,37,"Koo abo ni abalayi muno nohomba Abandu ba Tuba’ nende balia baliho imbeli wabu, khwabasishia toto abo bali abamabii"
  44,38,Ne efwe shikhwaloonga likulu nende bioosi bilimwo khumubayo tawe
  44,39,"Shikhwabiloonga tawe halali khubwatoto, ne abaanji mubo shibamanyile tawe"
  44,40,Toto inyanga yokhubusia ni ebise biarebwaho khuboosi
  44,41,"Inyanga yomwitsa alalikhoonya owashie nende shiosi shiosi tawe, ne shibalihabinwa tawe"
  44,42,Halali ulia owa Nyasaye alikoosia toto ye niwa Amaani Owobukoosia muno
  44,43,Toto omusaala kwa zaqoom
  44,44,Ni eshiakhulia shia owetsimbi
  44,45,"Shinga olubia lusaalulwe, lurabachila munda"
  44,46,Shinga okhurabachila khwa amatsi kayile
  44,47,"Baliboolelwa mbu : “mumutile mumusukune hakari wo mulilo kwa jahannam.”"
  44,48,Mana muyombole khumurwe kukwe eshinyasio shia amaatsi karabachila
  44,49,“Pila.. mbu newe (welolanga) Omwami woluyali
  44,50,Toto kano niko kamwakanakananga khwo
  44,51,Toto abaria Nyasaye baliba habundu womulembe
  44,52,Mwikulu mumikunda nende tsisebele
  44,53,Balifwala tsingubo tsinderere tsinyangu tsia hariri..nende tsisiro .. nibahengana
  44,54,"Endio nilwo lwakaliba, ne khulibabashila mahurul ain. (abakhana bomwikulu)"
  44,55,"Bali laangamwo ebiamo bietsimbia tsioosi, ne balikhala nomulembe"
  44,56,"Omo shibalipilamwo lifwa tawe, halali okhufwa khwokhuranga. Ne Nyasaye alibalinda okhurulana nende eshinyasio shia Jahanam"
  44,57,"Tsino nitsimbabaasi okhurula khu Nyasaye wuwo omulesi, okho nikho okhubura okhukhongo"
  44,58,"Ne efwe khwakhola Ikurani khululimi lulwo, okhuba inyangu khwiwe, kho banyoole okhwitsulila"
  44,59,Liinda nabo boosi baliinde butswa